{"tid":2460693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「傑斯」向高等法院申請保釋 杜麗冰拒絕 須繼續還押","createTime":"2021-03-25T03:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:06:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ed23bbb4ce5ec2e7c78a555bdd44817897122a2c","tid":2460693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"D100 網台主持人「傑斯」（原名尹耀昇）被指在節目引起他人憎恨、蔑視中港政府，被控 4 項「作出具煽動意圖的行為」罪，早前於西九龍裁判法院提堂，遭國安法指定法官、總裁判官蘇惠德拒絕保釋，還押至5 月 10 日再訊。「傑斯」其後向高等法院申請保釋，今由國安法指定法官杜麗冰處理，她聽罷雙方陳詞後，拒絕「傑斯」保釋，須繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n「傑斯」去年 11 月被捕，警方指控他發起的「千個爸媽，台灣助學」計劃涉嫌洗黑錢及資助分裂國家，他之後獲准保釋。今年 2 月 7 日，「傑斯」再次被警方國安處拘捕，指控他涉嫌「作出具煽動意圖的作為」罪。至 2 月 10 日，「傑斯」被指定法官蘇惠德拒絕保釋申請，由當日至今一直還押。<br />\n<br />\n被告尹耀昇（52 歲），被控違反第 200 章《刑事訴訟條例》第10 (1)(a) 條，惟案件由警方國安處負責。傑斯被控 4 項「作出具煽動意圖的行為」罪，指他於 2020 年 8 月 8 日，在香港連同其他人作出具煽動意圖的行為，即在一個網上節目作主持及演講，意圖引起憎恨或蔑香港特別行政區政府，或激起對其離叛，引起香港居民間的不滿或離叛，或慫恿他人不守法、不服從合法命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-4-%E9%A0%85%E4%BD%9C%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E7%BD%AA-%E5%82%91%E6%96%AF-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-4-%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=be4fc59d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-4-%25E9%25A0%2585%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%2F&h=2f95aab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-4-%E9%A0%85%E4%BD%9C%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E7%BD%AA-%E5%82%91%E6%96%AF-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92/</a>"},{"pid":"c1e24a217db877a5b836c3c17596c9ee5d5c55df","tid":2460693,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d275feb190fa76054a0306ee63f83c8388eb1e","tid":2460693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e24a217db877a5b836c3c17596c9ee5d5c55df","tid":2460693,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca44712227bf0aa80681e8fca22a3bb622758e2f","tid":2460693,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"唔比保又唔排期上庭審"},{"pid":"fa09b5bc43ccf8165f01728bdd51c43498a0e31a","tid":2460693,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"宜家港共擺明殺雞儆猴<br />\n打壓曬全部kol既言論自由"},{"pid":"962632c4640a76f09b24248e604084520823556a","tid":2460693,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T03:58:47.0